Class Counters.Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hama.bsp.Counters.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Counters.Counter>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    Enclosing class:
    Counters

    public static class Counters.Group
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, Iterable<Counters.Counter>
    Group of counters, comprising of counters from a particular counter Enum class.

    Grouphandles localization of the class name and the counter names.
